Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人一共三名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.53,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御伽银行选拔队
